35 m. Additional information about retirement and saving and other
36 information designed to promote financial literacy and capability
37 which may take the form of links to, or explanations of how to obtain,
38 such information.
39 n. How to obtain additional information about the Program.
40 "§ 143B-437.127. Protection from liability for covered employers.
41 (a) A covered employer or other employer is not and shall not be liable for or bear
42 responsibility for any of the following:
43 (1) An employee's decision to participate in or not to participate in the Program
44 or a participant's specific elections under the Program.
45 (2) Participants' or the Board's investment decisions.
46 (3) The administration, investment, investment returns, or investment
47 performance of the Program, including, without limitation, any interest rate or
48 other rate of return on any contribution or account balance, provided they play
49 no role.
50 (4) The Program design or the benefits paid to participants.
